</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
How timely. The Department of Trade and Industry is holding a one-day
seminar - A practical guide to UK export controls - on Friday.
The morning session will explore such delicate questions as Why Export
Controls?, while the afternoon session will involve a series of clinics
