FT  16 NOV 92 / CBI catalogues prompt payers
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
THE Confederation of British Industry today publishes a list of more than
400 organisations that are supporting its code of prompt payment practice in
an attempt to encourage companies not to delay payment of bills.
It is an A-Z guide ranging from AEA Technology and AIG Consultants to
Yorkshire Electricity Group and Zan.
Many large UK companies are not in the list, however, ranging from British
Aerospace and BOC to SmithKline Beecham and Wellcome.
Prompt Buyers - A Guide. CBI, Centre Point, 103 New Oxford Street, London,
WC1A 1DU. Free.
